    "id": "non-player-characters-npcs"
  }, "Non-Player Characters (NPCs)"), mdx("p", null, "No campaign or adventure is complete without monsters for the heroes to defeat or other types of adversaries for them to overcome. But it's best not to go alone, and often the characters will find help along the way. Collectively these friends and foes are called \u201CNPCs\u201D (non-player characters). When planning out a campaign or adventure, consider that the NPCs of your story typically fall into one of the following categories:"), mdx("ul", null, mdx("li", {
