    parentName: "p"
  }, "fatigued"), " bane."), mdx("p", null, mdx("strong", {
    parentName: "p"
  }, "Failure, but the story progresses:"), " Setting Sun's training was good, but the calm of the monastery is hard to recall amidst his current struggles. Overcome with hunger and thirst, the monk suffers 2 levels of the ", mdx("em", {
